{"tid":587793,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解馬會唔肯開本地波盤，振興香港足球運動？","createTime":"2018-03-10T16:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T09:39:38.000Z","uid":15935,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"514c756defc398964d141fecac502e84a40fdc6f","tid":587793,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T16:42:53.000Z","msg":"你睇下波台成日狗咬狗骨，當正隊波係自己條子孫根咁重要，未咒到對面陷家剷都唔肯收手就知香港人對足球係幾咁有熱誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n球隊可以有多啲投資，做好培訓，港足從此唔洗再比人恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等啲球隊打下假波可以促進經濟發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做莊嘅馬會又可以食晒班廢中廢老嘅身家，收資源再分配之效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間中比老廉冚一兩場港假，年度業績更加省鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n何樂而不為？"},{"pid":"5e76d925dca6bd62dff86745410b91bf1fcfc9fe","tid":587793,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T02:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c880b2c54c0bce174280b7a81a1f90827ac558f3","tid":587793,"uid":106641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T02:28:33.000Z","msg":"其實唔係馬會肯唔肯問題，係法例問題"},{"pid":"3aa7868d3386e29b02f6bcd37ebf3a9765c49d52","tid":587793,"uid":55458,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T02:48:04.000Z","msg":"賭玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129623469994f7622612092006644f8c4d6aa6ad","tid":587793,"uid":188,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T02:51:22.000Z","msg":"全香港有人識打波？"},{"pid":"ca4169204a7cb3a063e61f01a98378e7e95ff079","tid":587793,"uid":140802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T02:55:06.000Z","msg"